# GitHub Packages auth for the primary publish (auto/lerna `npm publish`). Read by the npm CLI at publish time only;
# pnpm ignores env-var auth in a committed .npmrc (GHSA-3qhv-2rgh-x77r) and resolves @alienfast/* from public npm.
# npmjs.org publishing uses OIDC trusted publishing — no token needed.
//npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_TOKEN}
